msgid "User Statistics by Region - SPCast Live"
msgstr "User Statistics by Region - SPCast Live"

msgid "Shows user activities by region. Detailed statistics for various time periods, daily and weekly."
msgstr "Juri l-attivitajiet tal-utent skont ir-reġjun. Statistika dettaljata għal diversi perjodi ta 'żmien, kuljum u kull ġimgħa."

msgid "User Statistics by Region"
msgstr "Statistika tal-Utenti skont ir-Reġjun"

msgid "View anonymized data on user activities in the SPCast network by region. These statistics show how usage is distributed geographically, based on daily and weekly evaluations."
msgstr "Ara d-dejta anonimizzata dwar l-attivitajiet tal-utent fin-netwerk SPCast skont ir-reġjun. Din l-istatistika turi kif l-użu huwa mqassam ġeografikament, ibbażat fuq evalwazzjonijiet ta’ kuljum u ta’ kull ġimgħa."

msgid "Shows the protocols of user activities in the network. Statistics for daily, weekly, and monthly evaluations."
msgstr "Juri l-protokolli tal-attivitajiet tal-utent fin-netwerk. Statistika għal evalwazzjonijiet ta' kuljum, ta' kull ġimgħa u ta' kull xahar."

msgid "View anonymized protocol statistics of user activities in the SPCast network. This data provides insights into the usage of technical protocols for various periods."
msgstr "Ara l-istatistika tal-protokoll anonimizzata tal-attivitajiet tal-utent fin-netwerk SPCast. Din id-dejta tipprovdi għarfien dwar l-użu tal-protokolli tekniċi għal diversi perjodi."

msgid "Statistics on the ports used by users in the network. Real-time data for daily and weekly analyses."
msgstr "Statistika dwar il-portijiet użati mill-utenti fin-netwerk. Dejta f'ħin reali għal analiżi ta' kuljum u ta' kull ġimgħa."

msgid "Anonymized statistics on the ports used by users in the SPCast network. This data helps to identify general trends and technical preferences of radio stations."
msgstr "Statistika anonimizzata dwar il-portijiet użati mill-utenti fin-netwerk SPCast. Din id-dejta tgħin biex jiġu identifikati tendenzi ġenerali u preferenzi tekniċi tal-istazzjonijiet tar-radju."

